oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Dolly Parton at Pinewood Christian Academy
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Metal photoplates; Parton, Dolly;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing the Grand Ole Opry star Dolly Parton with the Traveling Family Band, Jerry Jowers, and others at the Pinewood Christian Academy on May 2. Poster features a metal photoplate of Dolly Parton. Poster was printed for job no. 16388. To view the paperwork associated with this poster, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/28111.
